name: url_encode
description: URL-encodes the input. All characters are percent-encoded except for alphanumerics, `.`, `-`, `_`, and `~`. Spaces are encoded as `+`.
examples: ROW u = "https://example.com/?x=foo bar&y=baz" | EVAL u = URL_ENCODE(u)
